News24 Correspondent(Supplied by ER24) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Pretoria - The body of a man has been found on the N14 highway in Centurion, paramedics said on Sunday."Paramedics were returning to their branch [on Sunday morning], when they found a vehicle parked in the centre [of the highway]," said ER24 spokesman Russel Meiring.He said that the car belonged to bystanders who had stopped when they spotted the body in the road."[The man was] found to have sustained numerous injuries and showed no signs of life."A car believed to have belonged to the man was found parked further up the road.The circumstances surrounding his death are being investigated. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.